{"tid":1378777,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【只許成功】請停止將香港抗爭同六四比較","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:55:38.000Z","uid":2010,"like":236,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"839250d2e4f037035da4973e4fd8004b3f8e559b","tid":1378777,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:38:59.000Z","msg":"隔離post話香港重演緊六四，我認為並不適合，希望大家正評該post時多作思考：<br />\n<br />\n1. 1989與現今科技相差之遠，中共再次血腥鎮壓具有特殊地位嘅香港，所有舉動立即通天，後患一定比六四更嚴重，當然大家都必須謹記中國無冇血性；<br />\n<br />\n2. 六四之為失敗，係因為佢哋相信解放軍為人民服務、相信學生領袖與政權談判。喺呢一點上，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人嘅意識形態比中國人優勝好多</span></strong>，我哋嘅思想已進化到認清敵人、不靠大台，大家毋須自貶；<br />\n<br />\n3. 六四失敗之二，係中國學生／示持者明明有優勢（如：後期有槍械）但都冇運用，更遭到「自己友」（劉曉波等人）篤灰、割蓆、將槍枝比返政權。只要香港人保持團結，尤其係<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非給予勇武派更多支持及鼓勵</span>，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋同中國人嘅下場，絕對不同</span></strong>；<br />\n<br />\n4. 我哋已經認清香港冇回頭路，到咗point of no return，但中國學生仲相信可以改革中國政權。<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋並不似中國人般天真，我哋更為聰明，更識進步。</span></strong>不必同盲目相信共產政權嘅中國人比較。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5.<span style=\"color: red;\"> 我哋係香港人，唔係中國人</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>我哋搞嘅唔係咩「愛國民主運動」，而係反中反共、使香港重光嘅革命</strong></span>&mdash;&mdash;換言之我哋係更高層次，毋須與失敗者相比。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只許成功，不許回頭！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8d29ee4ee455e21ca7ea7feded127dccc9584a85","tid":1378777,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"045670ce3a748793f494c655ec39269841e5f68b","tid":1378777,"uid":2010,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:43:00.000Z","msg":"我哋搞嘅唔係咩「愛國民主運動」，而係反中反共、使香港重光嘅革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8182a8299aaf94c989d1e693477e639d88d6a6","tid":1378777,"uid":20059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:44:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"429eceb4c9b3939f0781ebd39ad78ccde75e9007","tid":1378777,"uid":51512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"4de8eef9686bb5f8af8f39ad6ab40f1ebeb4b977","tid":1378777,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcb36757194a8a538e4e9b0c4122ae1fafa99c3","tid":1378777,"uid":2010,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:47:47.000Z","msg":"中國並唔怕中國人，因為中國人到最後都係「愛國」、都相信「國家」係好嘅；<br />\n但係中國怕香港人，因為香港人越嚟越清楚所有禍害嘅根源係中國、中國係我哋嘅敵人，所以我哋反抗起嚟，比中國人更有效、更聰明、更中要害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c14716229d2f2402f3e4249374f82dc3ec781da","tid":1378777,"uid":160502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:52:21.000Z","msg":"中國=中共<br />\n係人都應該要知"},{"pid":"50a2c22942adc6e0b34ce82405900dabebbedd47","tid":1378777,"uid":2010,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:55:39.000Z","msg":"「以歷史為教訓」同「自我實現預言（歷史）」係兩回事，<br />\n隔離Po話6月3號有來歷不明嘅槍械、招致中共出兵等等暗謀論，<br />\n並唔係以史為鑑，而係想大家「自我實現預言」，<br />\n下次如果現場真係有武器，大家就會懼怕自己會好似六四咁失敗，<br />\n從而更為畏懼、唔再相信勇武手段。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真正嘅以歷史為教訓，係從歷史中認清「中國」呢個敵人嘅不堪，<br />\n唔好再心存倦倖、唔好諗住去感化，<br />\n並且不斷進步，唔好好似六四班人咁笨柒。</span><br />\n我哋好明顯係行緊同六四唔同嘅路，我哋正在一步一步咁邁向成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f657d7e270b60bc551e365eddbefc5e5333cbc","tid":1378777,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:55:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c2e7dfff3f02a414c18f39e340147f45b7269ad","tid":1378777,"uid":30688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:56:43.000Z","msg":"今次之後，香港要有真正嘅自治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98d80c5e96fb4bf810f55b8a195e41843a8dd44","tid":1378777,"uid":33783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:57:59.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"60985b7b3a44f7ca9cfdda19f8b55667bff00acc","tid":1378777,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:58:01.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔好畀失敗主義擴散"},{"pid":"d33d802975aec75408eb5846a30241bf26d2955f","tid":1378777,"uid":82152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:59:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f14b2d697d2252c40e59948fb45816cc7449dc0a","tid":1378777,"uid":2010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:59:41.000Z","msg":"請大家推上熱門，阻止宣揚「抗爭正步向失敗」嘅言論散播。"},{"pid":"a3f107f3616317f3180d02ad37800cfbbb69a4d1","tid":1378777,"uid":36481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:00:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"bb94ad27c090b5c5604a6eec9dd5f2ad483107dc","tid":1378777,"uid":29027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1e9e4df2b1b634e332fb6ef761e3dcf0a45dcf1","tid":1378777,"uid":270281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:02:18.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c127d5e429cb212454647d854631e3ef3ec052","tid":1378777,"uid":250580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:02:25.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n唔應該盲目咁自比六四 <br />\n背景同局勢同當年根本唔一樣 <br />\n有兩手準備冇壞<br />\n但提防有人spin去六四製造白色恐怖"},{"pid":"b1bcefe91797630fa66be2a6ce77d3502cce7b65","tid":1378777,"uid":2010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"大家毋須自貶<br />\n<br />\n正如立法會一役一樣，所謂敵人嘅「陰謀」、「陷阱」，<br />\n只要你識得發揮，比敵人去得更盡，<br />\n只要你唔會因為擔心中計而退縮，<br />\n再多嘅「陰謀」都會變成我方嘅